Package: tuner2
Type: Package
Title: Analyse and plot the vibration datasets from the NASA repository 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("david","redmond", email = "davidredmo531@yahoo.com", role =
    c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Analyses and plots the important features of motor bearing vibration data. 
    Options are to select from 2 datasets and to plot a sample, or all of the data.   
    The plots optiosn allow for more investigation of the selected features.
    Down load the nasa datasets and extract into your home account.
    A sample is available in the dataset directory
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: TRUE
